milestones.description: Tony Ura and Kiplin Doriga's 146-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 104 between Tony Ura and Kiplin Doriga
Tony Ura and Kiplin Doriga's 146-run partnership is PNG's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 112 between Hiri Hiri and Sese Bau
Norman Vanua has broken the record for most ducks (7) in ODIs for PNG, going past Sese Bau's 6
